  "slug": "no-bake-strawberry-cheesecake",
  "title": "No-bake strawberry cheesecake",
  "subtitle": "A set cream cheese filling on a biscuit base with fresh strawberries",
  "excerpt": "A no-bake cheesecake with a digestive biscuit base, a set cream cheese and double cream filling, and fresh strawberries on top. It goes into the fridge rather than the oven and sets firm enough to slice cleanly.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "No-bake cheesecake is a British domestic staple with roots in the American cream-cheese dessert tradition of the 1950s and 1960s, when refrigeration became widespread in homes. The digestive biscuit base is a British adaptation (replacing the American graham cracker). The set filling using whipped double cream rather than gelatine (the American method) is documented in Delia Smith's Complete Cookery Course (1978) and Nigella Lawson's How to Be a Domestic Goddess (2000).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "This is a cream cheese and double cream filling set over a crushed biscuit base, finished with fresh strawberries. No oven, no water bath. The filling sets through the fat in the cold cream and cream cheese firming up overnight. For it to slice cleanly, allow at least 6 hours in the fridge; overnight is better. Use a springform tin: a fixed base makes the cheesecake almost impossible to remove without breaking it."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "infoPanel",
        "attrs": {
          "type": "tip"
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Line the base with a circle of baking paper. The springform release lets the sides drop away cleanly."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": "Biscuit base"
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "digestive-biscuits",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": "crushed to fine crumbs",
                  "quantity": 200,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "unsalted-butter",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": "melted",
                  "quantity": 75,
